{"parentUuid":"4e652885-599e-491f-93ce-5893e7d5cba8","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a715a05a9db471dd5","message":{"id":"msg_202605181901552e4ebefee63745e5","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.5-air","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nBased on my knowledge of Claude Code and the information I can gather from your configuration, here's where Claude Code stores conversation history and session data:\n\n## Claude Code Conversation Storage Path on macOS\n\nClaude Code stores conversation history and session data in the following locations:\n\n1. **Project-specific conversation data**: In the `.claude/` directory within your project\n2. **Global conversation data**: Typically stored in `~/.claude/` in your home directory\n3. **Session data**: Also stored in these locations, usually in subdirectories like `sessions/` or `conversations/`\n\nThe exact path structure is typically:\n- `~/.claude/` - Global configuration and conversation storage\n  - `sessions/` - Session data\n  - `conversations/` or `history/` - Conversation history\n  - `cache/` - Cache files\n  - `logs/` - Log files\n\n## Transferring Conversations Between Machines\n\nTo transfer/resume a conversation on a different machine, you would need to copy:\n\n1. **Global configuration**: The entire `~/.claude/` directory from your source machine\n   - This includes all settings, conversation history, session data, and cache files\n\n2. **Project-specific conversations**: The `.claude/` directory from each project directory you want to resume conversations in\n\n3. **Authentication tokens**: Your ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN (if not already in your environment)\n\n**Important considerations when transferring:**\n- The target machine needs to have Claude Code installed\n- You may need to adjust file permissions after copying\n- Ensure the same model configuration exists on both machines\n- Any custom tools or skills would also need to be reconfigured on the target machine\n\nNote that conversation history may contain sensitive information, so be careful about how you transfer and store it."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":248,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":13816,"output_tokens":595,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"attributionAgent":"claude-code-guide","type":"assistant","uuid":"b3c08135-3812-4520-addb-7630af89f074","timestamp":"2026-05-18T11:02:03.702Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/soulhappy/gitclone/Kimi_Agent_企业AI智能体讲座","sessionId":"67036ab8-f39a-44b6-873e-b45adda17efb","version":"2.1.138","gitBranch":"main"}
